A 20-year-old mother-of-two was killed by a single gunshot wound and died in the street, authorities said.

Candace DeMoss was discovered lying on a patch of grass outside a home after police responded to reports of a shooting in the early hours of Sunday.

Her death is being investigated as a homicide by Cincinnati Police in Ohio after her body was found at 3.48am.Â 

