However they added that she had turned her life around, graduated from high school and was hoping to attend college.

Police have yet to release further details about the shooting which took place on the north side of the city.

Any one with information should call CrimeStoppers at 513-352-3040.

A funeral service for the young mother is yet to be arranged.

